---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Jernal | Daily Writing Prompts" description="Learn more about Jernal, why it was created, how daily writing prompt seeds work, and how you can reach out.">
  <div id="about-container">
    <div class="glass-container about-card">
      <h1 class="about-title">About Jernal</h1>
      <p class="about-tagline">We give you the prompt, you generate the story.</p>
      
      <hr class="divider" />
      
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Why I Built This</h2>
        
        <p>
          Jernal was created because I love writing and want to be constant in my practice of it. 
          However, I felt weird asking AI to generate prompts only for me to generate a response (the irony). 
          Jernal was born from that. All prompts are human made with the goal being that the responses be human generated. 
          While I think there is a time and a place for AI content, I do believe writing is best made by and for humans. 
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Writing is an art as much as painting, drawing, and sculpting. 
          They are expressions of human passions. Much like these, writing also needs constant practice to build upon better and 
          better techniques. I couldn’t find many apps, or websites, that I liked that had what I wanted: just a prompt and a text 
          box, so I decided to make one. 
        </p>

        <p>
          It’s not perfect by any means, and I hope to improve upon it in the future, but for now that’s basically all this is; 
          a prompt and a text box. A place for humans to use their ability to think and write out what they are thinking for 
          themselves, and possibly for others. I hope you enjoy it. 
        </p>

      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Daily Prompts</h3>
            <p>Every single day, two new prompts are made public. One fiction, and one personal reflection.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Privacy First</h3>
            <p>Write anonymously and copy your work, or save it to your profile. You control who sees your stories.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section contact-section">
        <h2>Contact Me</h2>
        <p>Have feedback, suggestions, or want to say hello? I'd love to hear from you!</p>
        
        <div class="contact-details">
          <a href="mailto:lehigraciaiii@gmail.com" class="contact-method">
            <div class="contact-icon-wrapper">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="contact-icon"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
              <span class="contact-label">Email</span>
              <span class="contact-value">lehigraciaiii@gmail.com</span>
            </div>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="contact-arrow"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lehi-gracia-966196273/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-method">
            <div class="contact-icon-wrapper">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="contact-icon"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
              <span class="contact-label">LinkedIn</span>
              <span class="contact-value">Lehi Gracia</span>
            </div>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="contact-arrow"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  #about-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 100px 1.5rem 40px 1.5rem; /* Space for navbar */
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    color: #ffffff;
    max-width: 800px !important;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-blue) 0%, var(--color-red) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin: -1rem 0 0 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .divider {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: #ffffff;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-blue);
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Features Grid styling */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    text-align: left;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-item:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .feature-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-blue-light);
  }

  .feature-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Contact details */
  .contact-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .contact-method {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    text-align: left;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #ffffff;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .contact-method::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 207, 193, 0.08) 0%, rgba(216, 30, 91, 0.08) 100%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .contact-method:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .contact-method:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .contact-icon-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--color-blue-light);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .contact-method:hover .contact-icon-wrapper {
    background: rgba(0, 207, 193, 0.15);
    border-color: var(--color-blue-light);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .contact-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .contact-value {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .contact-method:hover .contact-value {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .contact-arrow {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    transform: translateX(0);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .contact-method:hover .contact-arrow {
    color: var(--color-blue-light);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    #about-container {
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-top: 110px;
    }
    .about-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
